OL,6,FLine of Duty and Outlander star Brian
OL,7,FMcCardie has died aged 59, his agent
OL,8,Fhas confirmed.
OL,10,FHis sister Sarah McCardie announced on
OL,11,FTuesday that he died "suddenly at
OL,12,Fhome" on Sunday in a post on X.
OL,14,FThe Scottish actor, who grew up in
OL,15,FCarluke, near Glasgow, played criminal
OL,16,Fboss turned police informant Tommy
OL,17,FHunter in the hit BBC crime drama.
