OL,6,FMcCardie also had parts in Roman-set
OL,7,Fseries Domina as Cicero, time travel
OL,8,Fhistorical show Outlander as Sir
OL,9,FMarcus MacRannoch, who offers help
OL,10,Fduring a prison rescue attempt, and as
OL,11,Fthe Irish leader James Connolly in
OL,12,F1916-set Rebellion.
OL,14,FFollowing the post, United Agents
OL,15,Fconfirmed his death on X.
OL,17,FIn a statement, they said: "We are
OL,18,Fshocked and so deeply saddened by the
OL,19,Ftragic news of Brian's sudden death.
